freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I can still tell where I got the vaccination, but only if I rub my upper arm at the vaccination site.  It is virtually undetectable.
The only symptom I have had is minor soreness at the injection site - very minor.
Today, I can barely feel where my vaccination spot was.
